data.description: Experience the Serenity of the central Oregon Coast in this  2 bed 1 bath all one level home on 3.86 acres in Otis just 15 minutes to Lincoln City.  Newer Stainless steel appliances, Newer gas furnace, oversized laundry room, eat in kitchen/dining area, gas fireplace, master bedroom has large walk in closet.  Property is full of the natural trees and mature landscaping for added privacy.  Detached 1 car garage with new opener, Chicken coop, Covered porch, newer Trex decking, full house Generac back up generator.
